   "Commercial Use": Any use of the Software in a product or service offered for compensation, including paid services, subscription systems, licensing, resale, or other revenue-generating commercial activities.

   Sponsorship alone shall not constitute Commercial Use.

   However, the use of the Software in advertisement-supported services, services displaying advertisements, or services generating advertising revenue shall be considered Commercial Use.

